# Frontend Integration Patterns

## HTML Structure
The main dashboard is defined in [web_server.go](mdc:web_server.go) within the `handleHome` function.

### Layout Structure
- Single-page application with grid layout
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Fixed banner at bottom with scrolling content
- Modular sections for different data types

### Key CSS Classes
- `.main-layout` - Grid container for main content
- `.scoreboard-section` - Live game data display
- `.news-section` - NHL headlines feed
- `.mammoth-analysis-section` - Team performance analysis
- `.banner-container` - Fixed bottom scrolling banner

## HTMX Integration
- Use `hx-get` for dynamic content loading
- Target specific elements with `hx-target`
- Implement automatic refresh cycles
- Handle loading states and error conditions

### HTMX Patterns
```html
<!-- Dynamic content loading -->
<div hx-get="/news" hx-target="#news-content" hx-trigger="load"></div>

<!-- Manual refresh buttons -->
<button hx-get="/scoreboard" hx-target="#scoreboard-content">Refresh</button>

<!-- Automatic updates -->
<div hx-get="/banner" hx-target="#banner-content" hx-trigger="every 1h"></div>
```

## JavaScript Patterns
- Use `DOMContentLoaded` for initialization
- Implement automatic refresh cycles with `setInterval`
- Handle loading states and error conditions
- Use fetch API for JSON data (mammoth analysis)

### JavaScript Functions
```javascript
// Load functions for different data types
loadNews()           // Fetches and displays news
loadScoreboard()     // Updates live game data
loadMammothAnalysis() // Loads team performance data
loadBanner()         // Updates scrolling banner

// Automatic refresh cycles
setInterval(loadScoreboard, 30000);    // 30 seconds
setInterval(loadNews, 600000);         // 10 minutes
setInterval(loadMammothAnalysis, 1800000); // 30 minutes
```

## CSS Styling Guidelines
- Use CSS Grid for responsive layouts
- Implement backdrop filters for modern glass effects
- Use CSS animations for smooth transitions
- Maintain consistent color scheme and typography

### Color Scheme
- Primary: `#007bff` (blue)
- Success: `#28a745` (green)
- Warning: `#ffc107` (yellow)
- Danger: `#dc3545` (red)
- Background: `rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7-0.9)` (semi-transparent black)

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach with media queries
- Grid layout adapts to screen size
- Touch-friendly interface elements
- Optimized for various device orientations

## Content Formatting
- Use consistent HTML structure for data display
- Implement proper semantic markup
- Ensure accessibility with proper ARIA labels
- Use consistent date and time formatting

### HTML Templates
- Schedule data: `formatBannerHTML()`
- News headlines: `formatNewsHTML()`
- Scoreboard: `formatScoreboardHTML()`
- Team analysis: `formatMammothAnalysisJSON()`

## Performance Optimization
- Minimize DOM manipulation
- Use efficient CSS selectors
- Implement proper loading states
- Cache static assets appropriately
- Use background images for visual appeal
